  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of a wound care debridement product and a moisturizer on sacral pressure ulcer
      wounds
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Pressure ulcers on the sacral area will be applied with either a wound debridement product or
      a wound moisturizer product plus a gentle wound dressing to manage wound closure over a 2-3
      week period of treatment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
